item.title: CVE-2019-1003048|2024-08-05T03:07:16.841Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20prqa%20plugin
item.description: A vulnerability in Jenkins PRQA Plugin 3.1.0 and earlier allows attackers with local file system access to the Jenkins home directory to obtain the unencrypted password from the plugin configuration.
